title: The game of life & Philadelphia Eagles update with Ross Tucker
itunes:title: The game of life & Philadelphia Eagles update with Ross Tucker
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 by Ross Tucker who is doing his annual visit to Los Angeles! The guys did a rapid fire podcast by going through a number of topics including Ross's thoughts on the Eagles after visiting OTA's (8:35), will Eli Manning be the Week 1 starter for the Giants (18:19), favorite comedians and best current stand-up comics today (30:48), what Ross wants to eat while in Los Angeles (37:52), Pittsburgh vs Philadelphia (44:31) and Ross's easiest and hardest players he had to block in his career (56:08).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
